---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="KODŌ 아카이브 | 하이엔드 큐레이션">
  <div class="py-12">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-16 text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em]">
      <a href="/kr" class="text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors">← 인덱스로 돌아가기</a>
      <span class="text-white/20">케이스 스터디 / 이커머스 프로토타입</span>
    </div>

    <header class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6">KODŌ<br/>ARCHIVE</h1>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 border border-white/20 text-[9px]">하이엔드 아카이브</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 border border-white/20 text-[9px]">B2C 모델</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-end">
        <p class="text-xl leading-tight text-white/60">
          투자 가치가 있는 피스와 아카이브 패션 큐레이션. 희소성과 문화적 검증을 기반으로 한 비즈니스 모델.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 border-t border-white/10 pt-12">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[10px] text-white/30 tracking-widest mb-4 uppercase">타겟 세그먼트</h2>
          <p class="text-sm">NSE A/B. 하이 프로필 개인. 하이프 민감도가 높은 틈새 시장.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[10px] text-white/30 tracking-widest mb-4 uppercase">수익 모델</h2>
          <p class="text-sm">독점적 마진을 포함한 직접 판매 및 글로벌 소싱 물류.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-12">
        <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h2 class="text-[10px] text-white/30 tracking-widest mb-6 uppercase">구매자 페르소나: 루카 (27)</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            <p><span class="text-white/50 uppercase">위치:</span> 메리다 / CDMX / 글로벌 허브</p>
            <p><span class="text-white/50 uppercase">동기:</span> 완전한 독점성과 급진적 정체성.</p>
            <p class="sm:col-span-2"><span class="text-white/50 uppercase">행동:</span> 재판매 가치가 높은 패션 자산에 투자.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-12 border-t border-white/5">
          <h2 class="text-[10px] text-white/30 tracking-widest mb-8 text-center underline uppercase">아이템 컨디션 프로토콜</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <div class="border border-white/10 p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-[9px] text-white/40 mb-2 uppercase">원단</p>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase font-bold">S 등급</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-white/10 p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-[9px] text-white/40 mb-2 uppercase">하드웨어</p>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase font-bold">A 등급</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-white/10 p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-[9px] text-white/40 mb-2 uppercase">스티칭</p>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase font-bold">변경 없음</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-white/10 p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-[9px] text-white/40 mb-2 uppercase">정품 인증</p>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase font-bold">인증됨</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-32 space-y-32">
      <div class="space-y-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 group overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img src="/images/kodo-home.png" alt="데스크톱 인터페이스" class="w-full h-auto grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 antialiased" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-[9px] text-white/20 italic tracking-[0.2em] text-center uppercase">01 // UI 아키텍처: "럭셔리는 죽었다" 컨셉</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto items-end">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 shadow-xl">
            <img src="/images/kodo-apparel.jpg" alt="큐레이션 선택" class="w-full h-auto opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
          </div>
          <p class="text-[9px] text-white/20 italic tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-right">02 // 큐레이션: 아카이브 의류 (Heliot Emil)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 md:pb-24">
          <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 shadow-xl">
            <img src="/images/kodo-items.jpg" alt="아이템 인벤토리" class="w-full h-auto opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
          </div>
          <p class="text-[9px] text-white/20 italic tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">03 // 인벤토리: 투자 자산 그리드</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto border-t border-white/5 pt-16">
        <h2 class="text-[10px] text-white/30 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-center">모바일 생태계 및 전환 흐름</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-start">
          <div class="space-y-4">
              <img src="/images/kodo-cart.jpg" alt="장바구니 UX" class="w-full h-auto border border-white/10 shadow-2xl" />
              <p class="text-[8px] text-white/20 italic uppercase text-center">04 // 트랜잭션 UX: 체크아웃 로직</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 md:mt-24">
              <img src="/images/kodo-registration.jpg" alt="사용자 등록" class="w-full h-auto border border-white/10 shadow-2xl" />
              <p class="text-[8px] text-white/20 italic uppercase text-center">05 // 온보딩: 커뮤니티 액세스</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
              <img src="/images/kodo-form.jpg" alt="컨시어지 폼" class="w-full h-auto border border-white/10 shadow-2xl" />
              <p class="text-[8px] text-white/20 italic uppercase text-center">06 // 컨시어지 서비스: 직접 채널</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="mt-32 pt-12 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-white/40 italic uppercase tracking-widest">2단계: 전략 및 큐레이션 활성화</p>
        <a href="https://kodoarchive.myshopify.com/" target="_blank" class="bg-white text-black px-8 py-3 text-xs font-bold hover:invert transition-all">
            SHOPIFY 프로토타입 보기 ↗
        </a>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>